meta.methodology: Fantrax FPts formula: PTS + REB + AST*2 + STL*4 + BLK*4 + FGM*2 - FGA + FTM - FTA + 3PM - TO*2. Pre=trade season, Post=next full season. Combined: 60% player delta + 40% pick slot grade (mixed), 100% for player-only or pick-only.
meta.scoring_source: basketball-reference.com per-game stats, converted to Fantrax scoring
